	* modules/irc-channel/irc-channel.c: fixed incorrect join parsing in
	  _ircch_recheck_link().
	* modules/autolog/autolog.c: fixed couple of bugs where got SIGSEGV.

Thu Oct  9 2008 Andriy Gritsenko <andrej@rep.kiev.ua>
